ygData.subject: Re: urgh
ygData.msgSnippet: Invisible hole? If it s a bug u can  page GM, otherwise it will be better to make a shout to request other powerful players to escort u back to retrieve ya
ygData.messageBody:
Invisible hole? If it's a bug u can page GM, otherwise it will be better
to make a shout to request other powerful players to escort u back to
retrieve ya corpse.

Ziltus
